ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a weekly meeting with the graduate students and undergraduate students helping in the lab where we practice presenting our own research but also discuss current topics in behavioral neuroscience. I would recommend this course to students because of the opportunities it presents and the papers we read and discuss are always interesting.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Of all of the courses I took this semester, I think this course contributed most to my research. I was able to talk to both Dr. Schafe but also the other graduate students in the lab about my research and get feedback from them collectively.
